com.antigenomics.alisa.algebra

Class LinearSpaceObjectArray<O extends LinearSpaceObject<O>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.antigenomics.alisa.algebra.LinearSpaceObjectArray<O>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - linear space object type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImmutableLinearSpaceObject<LinearSpaceObjectArray<O>>, LinearSpaceObject<LinearSpaceObjectArray<O>>, TypedCloneable<LinearSpaceObjectArray<O>>, Encoding, Representation, Serializable, Iterable<O>

    public class LinearSpaceObjectArray<O extends LinearSpaceObject<O>>
extends Object
implements LinearSpaceObject<LinearSpaceObjectArray<O>>, Iterable<O>
    An array of linear space objects. Supports elementwise addition and multiplication operations, including their in-place versions. Throws exceptions in case certain types of addition operations are not supported by a given linear space object type, or if there is a mismatch between array sizes.
